inn1.comm: and he begins with a beauty, great seam position, lands on off and moves past Hayden's bat, a cracker
fuller on middle and leg, moves in, Hayden plays and gets hit down the pad, ball trickles to the on side
short of a good length on middle and leg, worked to midwicket
middle and off this time, Hayden back and across in defense
fuller on off stump, Hayden looks to work it to leg but doesnt time it well, ball rolls to short midwicket
fuller this time, overpitched on middle and off, easily flicked in the gap at midwicket for four and Australia and Hayden are away, Agarkar ends a very good over with a boundary
this one's short outside off stump and he stands tall and glides that in the gap near gully for one
pitches outside off and moves away, near to being called a wide
good ball outside off, no room to cut and Hayden shoulders arms
outside off again, keeps low as Hayden leaves it
lands on leg and moves down Hayden's pad, Dhoni takes it as Munaf appeal, ball clipped the thigh pad
full outside off, left alone with caution
down the leg side, wide called
lands outside off on a full length and is left alone
overpitched on leg, looks to flick but gets rapped on the pads, they get a leg bye to backward square leg
middle and leg line again, worked to the left of Mongia at midwicket for a sharp single
full on off, Hayden presents the full face of the bat as he pushes it to mid-off
good length on off, quickly gets into position and pushes to mid-off for a quick single to retain the strike
shot, gives him the charge, adjusts at the end as he isn't to the pitch, keeps the head still and checks his stroke, ball races between Munaf and the stumps for four down the ground
a good length outside off, left alone
shorter outside off, some move on it, he shoulders arms
served up in the slot outside off, Hayden eases into his shot, drives it on the up n the gap at extra cover and the ball races away to the fence
good comeback, this lands on off on the seam and beats Hayden's forward prod
another good ball, pitches outside off and jags back sharply as Hayden shoulders arms, misses clipping the top of off stump
full outside off and its left alone for Dhoni
this one's also full outside off and Katich has a look and lets it pass
a no-ball, overpitched on off and its driven into the covers
full on off, Katich looks to flick and gets an inside edge around the corner and down to Munaf at fine leg
good length on middle and off, turned quickly to Mongia at midwicket
lands outside off and swings in close to off stump, Hayden knows where his stumps are and shoulders arms
fuller this time on middle and off, flicked on the up past mid-on for four and once again Agarkar gives a boundary off the last ball of an over
full outside off and its left alone
again overpitched outside off and Katich raises the bat to allow it to pass
slightly shorter in length but not enough to cut, Katich plays at it and is beaten
wide and full outside off, left alone
a great ball on and around off, pitches and seams past his bat
short of a length on the stumps, Katich stands and looks to work it fine but doesnt time it well, ball just drops at his feet, Munaf runs in to collect
full outside off, he goes for a drive but ends up mis-timing it back to Agarkar in his follow-through
good length on off, he stands and runs it down past gully for a single
fuller outside off, flashed at, ball goes in the air to point but bounces in front of the fielder
full again and its driven to mid-off where RP singh dives to his left and saves a certain four, good work
overpitched in the exact same spot but Hayden won't miss out, plants the foot forward and punches that past RP for four
identical ball, this time he can only drive it to the man at cover
good shot, full outside off, he drives that between the stumps and mid-off for four
better ball, lands on a good length outside off as he stands and shoulders arms

very good ball, lands just outsied off, seams in, Katich is caught on the crease, goes for a shot but gets rapped high on the pad, looked very close, everyone appeals but the umpire says no, what was wrong with that one?
full and defended to the off
full again, he looks to drive but gets an inside edge to square leg
pitches outside off and swings away, ignored
full on off, pushed to short extra cover

what a catch! Full outside off, Katich flays at it, ball speeds in the air and looks destined for four, but out of the blue dives Raina at point and simply pouches that with two hands going to his left, that ball was travelling at some speed but he did extremely well to intercept it, India get a breakthrough!
good length on off, defended to point

full length outside off, poked at and gets a thick edge right where a second slip should have been, thats a life, Tendulkar at first slip may have been able to make it with a sharp move to his left but he doesnt even make an attempt
full outside off, left alone
again outside off and left alone for Dhoni, a successful over comes to an end, could have been a second wicket there
what a ball, lands on a good length on off, Ponting lunges at that but is beaten all ends up
fuller on off, Ponting gets to it this time and defends with a dead bat
a driveable length on off, he gets forward and pushes that to Raina at point
good length on off, Ponting hops in his crease and defends to the on side, Munaf moves forward and collects
short on middle and off, works it with ease past square leg, Agarkar in the deep is slow and runs around the ball, they get a brace
pitches on a good spot outside off, Ponting forward and shoulders arms
pitches outside off and seams away, wide signalled, a close call
this one too lands outside off and Hayden leaves it alone
identical delivery, good seam position, Agarkar varying his pace here, Hayden leaves it alone
fuller this time outside off, Hayden looks to work it onside but can only drive to Harbhajan Singh at mid-on
wide of off stump again, some good pace and bounce on that one, umpire calls wide again
better, pitches on a good length outside off, stands tall and punches to mid-off, they steal a sharp single
good ball, full on off, Ponting into his stride, goes to work it to leg but closes the face of the bat and gets an edge to the offside and they get a run
short and wide outside off, flayed at and they get two down to third man, well run

got 'em! Fullish on the legs, Ponting whips that off the pads high in the air, doesnt keep it down, ball goes up and comes down to Agarkar at deep fine leg who takes a simple catch, Munaf gets his man
good ball on off, Martyn is forced to defend back to the bowler
close! Fullish outside off, he defends, ball thuds into the pad, but there was an inside edge on that one, lucky Martyn, unlucky Munaf&
fullish on middle and leg, flicked around the corner
a good length outside off, Hayden looks to drive but the ball hits the bat and drops at his feet, rolls to the off side and Munaf collects
and he begins with a good ball, pitches on off and carries on over the top of middle and off as Martyn shoulders arms
another good ball, stump-to-stump, Martyn just drops the bat on that one
this one nips into Martyn, the offcutter, he's squared up and rapped on the inner thigh, but it pitched outside the line of leg and middle
good ball, lands outside off and seams away, Martyn lets it through but this was close to the top of off stump
angles across him and he shoulders arms once again, RP hitting that sweet spot regularly, tying him down
a good ball to end a good over, lands on off and Martyn defends it back to the bowler
good ball on off, punched to point who swoops in and stops the run
advances down the track to one outside off, punched to Harbhajan at mid-off who misfields but Martyn had already turned his back so no run
one step down to one outside off and played to cover
short and wide and its well cut in the gap between point and cover for four

better ball, angles in from outside off, Hayden stands and drops the bat, ball rolls towards midwicket, they sprint for a run, fielder runs in and shies at the nonstriker's end but misses fractionally, that was close
short of a length outside off, driven off the backfoot past covers, Raina gives chase and slides on the ropes but messes it up and allows the boundary
full on off, driven back to the bowler, not fielded cleanly
fullish on middle and off, tapped towards mid-on for a quick single
driveable length outside off, pushed to Raina at cover
good ball on a length, stands tall and defends, loud call of 'NO' back to his partner
another good length ball on the stumps, patted back to the bowler who fields to his left
another good ball on off, defended into the covers
good length, pitches on middle and spins across Hayden who defends on the back foot
pitches outside leg stump, Hayden goes forward and defends
dabbed on the leg side on the front foot, Hayden wants the single but decides against it
worked off the pads through midwicket for one
tossed up on off and middle, Martyn steps down and works it off his pads to short fine leg
full on the pads, driven to mid-on for one
short of a length angling into Hayden from outside off stump, played to wide mid-on for one
angling across Martyn  from over the wicket, defended to point
good length on off stump, Martyn gets forward and defends
short of a length angling just outside off stump, Martyn pushes it towards cover on the front foot, he ddn't get to the pitch off that ball and played away from his body
shorter in length and outside off stump, kept a touch low as well, Martyn tries to force it through the off side but bottom edges it down to third man
angling into Hayden's pads, flicked wide off midwicket for one
just short of a length on leg stump, flicked but straight to square leg
pitches outside leg stump and angles into the pads, played to short fine leg
tossed up on leg stump, Hayden goes half forward and the ball hits his pads
on leg stump again, pushed on the front foot wide off mid-on for one
flatter ball but drifting on to Martyn's pads, played to wide mid-on again for one
quicker ball on leg stump, Hayden goes back to play it on the leg side but gets hit on the pads
good length outside off stump and moves away from Martyn who gets drawn into an airy drive and gets beaten
shorter length this time and Martyn cuts hard off the back foot, he should have put that away for four but found point
full length and that cut back into Martyn after pitching outside leg stump, Martyn is hit on the pad and the Indians go up in appeal
played behind square on the off side for one
angling into Hayden from outside off stump, the batsman gets forward and punches down the ground to mid-off for one
full and swinging back to Martyn who drives it back at RP Singh, the bowler picks up and fires it back at Martyn who turns his back to it and gets hit on the arm
driven to mid-off for one
good length on off stump and that spins back into Martyn who gets forward and pushes on the off side
off stump line, dabbed short of covers for a very quick single
pitches outside leg stump, Hayden steps down but isn't to the pitch of the ball and gets hit on the pad
full on the pads, flicked wide of mid-on for one
Martyn takes a step down, Harbhajan pushes it through flatter on off stump, the batsman defends towards cover
pitches on middle and leg and slips down leg side, wide called

India miss two run out chances! Full outside off stump, Hayden drove it on the up to mid-off, Martyn sets off from the non-strikers end but Hayden sends him back, the throw from mid-off misses the stumps or Marty would have been out, the fielder at midwicket fieldeded the ball and shied at the stumps but missed again or Martyn would still have been out
beaten outside the off stump
pushed to mid-on where Harbhajan mis-fields and concedes two
lofted over midwicket, that was a no-ball short of a length and Hayden powers it over the infield to move on to 49
driven down the ground for one and thats his fifty, he was out for 49 in the last game against West Indies, this time he reaches 50
played to point for one
width offered outside off stump and Hayden playes the square drive to the fence
tossed up on off and middle, Martyn uses his feet, takes a step down and turns it to midwicket

a disastrous mix-up! Martyn dabbed that short on the off side, he sets off, stops and then goes for the run because Hayden kept coming. The throw came to the keeper's end and Hayden was well short even though he dived
picthes outside off stump and turns into Symonds, defended on the leg side
played to midwicket on the front foot
drifts on to the pads, Symonds misses the flick and the ball goes to square leg off the pad
full and down leg side, Martyn pushed his pads out at it and padded it away
short of a length on off stump, driven on the up wide off mid-off for one
dropped the ball down at his toes and set off for a quick run
carved over point for six! That was far too short and wide outside off stump, Martyn frees his arms and launches it over the point fence
played in front of point on the front foot
slower ball on middle and leg stump, Symonds gets forward and pushes it to midwicket for one
flighted delivery on off stump, Symonds takes a step down and defends
full outside off stump, Symonds bashes it back to the bowler on the front foot, Harbhajan does well to dive to his left and field it
pitches on off, bounces and hits Symonds, who plays back at it, high on the thigh
defended back to the bowler
defended on the leg side on the front foot
a straighter one to end the over! Symonds played for the turn on the front foot but the ball beats the outside edge of his forward defense
defended on the front foot on the off side

another run-out! Martyn dabbed that close on the off side and set off for the single, Raina ran in from point and fired the throw in at the bowler's end, Mongia didn't collect it properly but the ball bounced off his hands to hit the stumps and Martyn was just short

Mongia strikes with his third ball! That pitched in line, went straight through with the arm, Symonds played for turn and got hit dead in front, Asad Rauf took his time and eventually raised the finger
defended back to the bowler
played down the ground for one
defended on the front foot
pushed to wide mid-off for one

That was almost the third run-out of the innings! Hussey turns it past square, there was an easy single but the second was suicide! Haddin was woefully short when the throw came into Harbhajan who whipped off the bails at the non-strikers end, Haddin was initially given out but replays showed that Harbhajan had broken the stumps without the ball in his hand
defended to point on the front foot
full outside off stump, dug out back to the bowler
tossed up on off stump, defended on the front foot
driven trhough cover on the front foot for a single
defended on the front foot
flicked wide of midwicket for one
pushed through quicker outside off stump, Haddin goes forward but the balls spins into him and hits the pad before going towards slip
tossed up on off stump and it drifts into Haddin who tries to flick but gets hit on the  pad outside the line of off stump
hit on the pad again outside the line of off stump, Haddin got forward to that but wasn't to the pitch of the ball
defended on the front foot
full on off stump, Haddin tries to drive but gets an inside edge past the fielder at short leg for a single
full outside off stump, the batsman steers it to first slip
full on off stump, driven firmly down the ground but RP Singh dives across from mid-off to cut off the boundary
turned to square leg for a single
full on off stump, Haddin uses his feet to step down and drive to mid-on
defended on the off side
driven back to the bowler on the front foot
shorter in length on off stump, Haddin drives off the back foot back to Mongia
tossed up on leg stump, Hussey goes down on one knee and sweeps fine, the fielder on the boundary at fine leg runs across and dives but the ball beats him
outside off stump, slightly short, cut to deep point, Munaf Patel saves the four with his foot
pushed to midwicket
tossed up on of and middle stump, pushed down the ground for one
tossed up on off stump from round the wicket, Hussey gets forward and defends it with an angled bat behind square on the off side
drifting into Hussey on a good length, the batsman gets a big stride in and defends
tossed up on off stump, Haddin uses his feet and drives past silly mid on for one
slower through the air, Hussey waits for it and defends watchfully
tight line just outside off stump, defended on the front foot
that bounces a little extra from the rough just outside off stump, Hussey is beaten by the lift and gets hit on the pad
guided to short third man for one
tossed up on off stump, Haddin closes the face too early and gets an outside edge behind square on the off side
slower through the air outside off stump, Hussey lets it go
drifts into Hussey from round the wicket, draws the batsman forward and spins away, Hussey prods at it but gets beaten

this time Harbhajan finds the edge much to Dravid's delight! That drifted into Hussey and he closed the face of the bat a bit too early, the ball spun away from him and took the outside edge to first slip where Dravid took a waist-high catch
tossed up outside off stump, Hogg pushes wide off the fielder at cover for a quick single
fuller in length, Haddin uses his feet to flick through midwicket for one
flighted delivery on middle stump, Haddin steps down and drives firmly to long-on for one
short ball on middle and leg stump, poor delivery, Hogg plays back and works it behind square for one
tighter line on off stump, defended back to the bowler
Haddin charges and charges well, he got down the pitch and freed his arms to loft it over long-off's head for six
driven wide off mid-on for one
pushed through quicker and flatter, short of a length, Hogg defends off the back foot
flatter ball on off stump, defended on the front foot
tossed up this time, defended on the front foot from off stump
pushed wide off mid-on but the fielder does well to cut it off
worked through wicket for one
tossed up, pitches outside off stump and spins away, Hogg thrusts it's pad at it
left alone outside off stump
tossed up outside off stump, driven hard to cover where Kaif dives to his right and makes a superb save
on middle and off stump, Haddin uses his feet to drive to long-on for one
defended on the back foot
short of a length, Hogg plays back at it and tries to turn it on the leg side, he gets a leading edge that loops short of midwicket
driven off the back foot through extra cover for a single
from around the wicket, tossed onto middle and off, pushed to cover
width offered outside off and its cracked to extra cover
back to over the wicket, middle and leg, turned to midwicket
off stump line, good flight, goes to cut but misses
tossed up outside off, Haddin back and defends to cover
flatter outside off, Hogg back and across and works it to mid-on for one
looped up on middle and off, he advances but ends up dead-batting it back to he bowler
middle and leg, flighted, worked to midwicket for another single
tossed up on off stump, defended to point and they steal a run
tossed up on off again, pushed into the covers
tossed up on off, Hogg back and across and pushes to cover
middle and leg and its patted back to Sehwag
short on middle and off, Hogg back away and cuts that sweetly in front of square, anticipated more turn but times it well and picks up four, good shot
another short ball and he rocks back and square cuts that hard, Munaf cant stop it on the ropes, four more
good shot! Tossed up on middle and leg, he advances down the track and swipes that over long-on for maximum, aggression here from Hogg!
short and its cut past point for a single
tossed up, advances and defends it back
defended back to Sehwag again
too flat and he works it to midwicket for a single
flat again but he stands and defends to cover
tossed up on middle and off, Hogg gets forward and looks to flick, ball goes wide of Sehwag who moves across to stop but cant get to it and they steal a quick run
a no-ball, tossed up on off and he goes back and gently pushes in front of point
quicker ball on off, pushed to point again
short and wide, cut in the vacant gap on the off side, Munaf has some work to do on the ropes and they get a couple
middle and leg, worked to midwicket who fields well
middle and off, defended
tossed up on off, Hogg steps forward and pushes that past Sehwag to long-off for  one
tossed up, gives the charge and hits that in the air past mid-on down to Patel at wide long-on for one to keep the strike
drifts into middle and leg, again he advances but ends up defending as he wasnt to the pitch of it
six more! Tossed up, he advances once more, not to the pitch of it by any reason but he's got some power and clears the man at long-on for maximum
the same result! Tossed up on middle and leg, Haddin charges and picks it up sweetly for six more over wide long-on this time, Mongia under the gun
tossed up on off, defended
flatter this time, he steps down and adjusts his stroke to defend
a no-ball, he goes forward and plays back to Mongia
flatter on the stumps, pushed back to Mongia, expensive over&
short and wide, cut past point for one with ease
short of a length on middle and off, tucked up and he pushes to the on side
beaten! Lands on a sweet spot on off and sits up as Haddin drives off the back foot and misses
middle and leg and moving down, Haddin looks to run it off the pads, ball clips the back leg and Dhoni lets it through his gloves, that's legbyes, poor from bowler and keeper
middle and off, Haddin stands and defends
dragged in short outside off, Haddin swivels and pulls, not timed well but he gets one anyway
short, he advances and drives that down to mid-off for one
fuller on off, Hogg stands and defends, ball shoots to point
middle and off, defended to the off side
good ball, fullish outside off and seaming in, Hogg pokes at it and gets beaten
bad ball down the pads
middle and off, pushed to mid-on for one
fullish on middle and leg, went to flick but mistimed and the ball clips the pads and rolls to square leg who moves in quickly
slow ball outside off, Hogg tries to cut but the ball dies on him and he misses
again there's width to cut, he chops that on the bounce to point
beats the outside edge, lands outside off, Hogg pushes but makes no contact
width offered again, Hogg slashes that past a diving Raina at point and gets one down to the sweeper
width again, Haddin uppercuts that in the gap at gully down to third man for one
good length delivery on middle and off, Hogg makes room and punches that towards point, sets off a run, Raina swoops in and underarms the throw on the stumps but Haddin was in
fullish on off, pushed back down the track to the bowler
good length ball on off, Hogg goes back and pushes that to mid-off
good length on middle and off, he steps down and frees the arms and drives that inside-out past mid-off for his first four

caught! Dragged in a little short, Haddin looks for the pull but gets hurried into the shot, his feet didnt really go anywhere either and he ends up slogging that straight up in the air for Dhoni to take a few steps forward and to his right and pouch the catch, Haddin's crucial innings comes to an end
short of a length, driven past point for a brace, Sehwag fields on the fence
full on middle and leg, moving down, clipped past square leg to deep backward square for one to retain the strike
short on middle and leg, worked to square leg for one
good length outside off, driven off the backfoot into the gap on the offside to get off the mark
bad ball, useless really, down the pads for Dhoni to collect
good ball on middle and off, cramps him for room, pushed in front of point and Lee is quick to call for the run
fires in the fullish delivery on middle and leg, well dug out into the vacant deep midwicket region for two, well run
shorter and he hops back to turn it fine, gets an inside edge down to backward square leg
shorter outside off, pushed in front of point to where Raina gets over the ball and gives away a single
full outside off and he watches it through to Dhoni
drifts onto middle and leg and the ball clips the pad for a legbye
good length ball on the stumps, Lee is quick into his defense, worked over RP and they steal a single as mid-on and mid-off converge
shorter on middle and leg and moving down, Hogg walks across his stumps to  heave it way but misses and Dhoni collects
full and slow outside off, Hogg dabs it in front of Raina at point and responds well to Lee's call for a single

run out! Full on the stumps, in the slot, Lee makes room and crunches that straight back down the ground, RP sticks his left hand out in the follow-through and gets a finger to it, ball ricochets onto the stumps and Hogg is well out of his crease and has to go, an unfortunate end to a good innings
a driveable length outside off and he does so with a firm push into the covers
full outside off, driven hard past covers, thought about two but they resist as Sehwag fires in an angry throw
slow on middle and off, agriculturally swung across the line for one to wide of mid-on
full again outside off and its driven to extra cover for just a single
wide, banged in short and angling down leg, Clark down on his haunches as the ball passes him

clean bowled! Fuller and straight on the stump, Clark just stands and has a swipe across the line, misses everything and the ball crashes into middle stump, a typical you-miss-I-hit dismissal, Australia are nine down
half-volley on off, pushed to mid-off, end of a good over from Agarkar

last man down! Fired in quickly on a good length around middle stump, Lee has a heave at it but doesn't time it cleanly and ends up hitting it straight down Sehwag's throat at deep square leg, Australia are bowled out inside 50 overs for 213

inn2.comm: good length on middle stump, Sehwag gets an inside edge on to the pad towards square leg, Lee goes up in appeal but there was a definite inside edge
angling into his pads, worked behind square on the leg side for one
good length, pitches wide of off stump and moves away from Tendulkar who lets it go
beats the outside edge! That pitched just short of a length on off stump and moves a fraction away, Tendulkar squares up and defends but the ball whizzes past the outside edge
overpitched outside off stump, Tendulkar reaches out for it and drives through gully for four
the batsmen call for the run, then hesitate and finally decide against it. That was short of a length on middle and leg and bounced off the pad towards midwicket
short and wide outside off stump, Sehwag cuts it over slips down to third man

gone, McGrath strikes first ball! or is it? Tendulkar tried to pull that ball which was banged in short, he missed the pull and was hit on the shoulder and Haddin collected the ball, the Australians appealed for the catch and the umpire at the bowlers end gave it out initially, then Tendulkar was called back for some reason, Ricky Ponting is livid
left alone outside off stump
pitches outside off stump and moves away, left alone
good length outside off stump, that rises on Tendulkar who leans out of the way
width offered outside off stump, cut off the back foot to third man
caught, and this time he won't be called back, short of a length outside off stump and Tendulkar drives but doesn't control it, the ball slices off the bat and goes straight to Hussey at point
fullish length outside off stump, Kaif lets it go
straighter ball, pitching on off and holding its line, Kaif defends towards cover
snorter! Lee revs up the pace and makes the ball rise from just short of a length, Kaif swerves out of the way
fuller and it nips back into Kaif and hits him high on the pad
short and width on offer outside off stump, Sehwag drives through cover but doesn't time it well enough for it to reach the fence
very wide outside off stump, going wider, Sehwag slashes and misses, wide called
shorter length and angling into the pads, flicked through square leg off his pads for two
short and wide of off stump, Sehwag is on to it in a flash and cuts down to third man
pitches wide outside off stump and moves further away, that's the second wide of the over
third wide, this time McGrath bangs it in short and it slips down leg side
McGrath's wide counter ticks over to four, sprayed outside off stump this time
drifting into the pads from short of a length, worked behind square for one
good length outside off stump, Sehwag backs away and tries to cut but gets beaten
short and wide outside off stump again, Sehwag cuts straight to Hussey at point, he will be disappointed not to put that away
pitches outside off and moves away, Kaif lets it go past
full an swinging into Kaif's pads, the batsman flicks it through midwicket for one
full and on Sehwag's pads this time, he whips it past square leg for two
knocked him over! Fast, pitches on off and nips in a touch, Sehwag plays outside the line and the ball crashes into off stump
pitches outside off stump, Dravid lets it go
pitches wide outside of and moves away, Dravid shoulders arms
just short of a length outside off, defended to mid-off
in the corridor outside off stump, Kaif plays off the back foot to McGrath
this time McGrath moves the ball away from Kaif from just outside off stump, Kaif wafted at it and was comprehensively beaten
now he nips it back into Kaif from just outside off, Kaif lets it go but that was close to off stump
pitches outside off and goes straight on, Kaif gets forward and defends
shorter in length and just outside off, Kaif tries to punch off the back foot but times it poorly, McGrath follows up a disastrous second over with a maiden
good length, fast and straight, Dravid dabs it on the leg side for a quick single
pitches on off and middle, pitches on a good length at furious pace and seams away from Kaif who can do little else but get squared up and beaten
full and drifting on to the pads, flicked through midwicket but it's not timed well
short in length and drifting down leg side, Kaif moves across and tickles it down to the fine leg fence
driven on the up to mid-off, Martyn gets across but dives over the ball and concedes runs
short of a length on off stump, Kaif stands up and defends to point
on a good length, angling into middle and leg from just outside off, defended to midwicket
defended on the back foot back to McGrath
pitches just outside off on a good length and rises into Dravid's hips, the batsman goes back and defends
short  and wide outside off stump, Dravid goes back, waits for it and punches through covers for four
tighter line, homing into off from just outside, defended back to the bowler
short of a length and just outside off stump, Dravid plays it on the back foot to point
short and wide outside off stump, Kaif punches through covers on the back foot, Hussey does well to drag it back on the fence
defended back to the bowler
just outside off stump and angling into Kaif who has no room to play with, defended on the front foot
climbs on Kaif from just short of a lenth outside off stump, Kaif stands tall and punches to point on the back foot
wide outside off stump and Kaif initially wanted to play at it and then pulled out at the last moment, the ball hits the bat and rolls to slips
chopped to third man on the back foot, that was a little to wide of off stump
